  * [https://docs.google.com/leaf?id=0B6p_m8EvqxeuNzhiMGJmZDAtNTI5YS00Nzk5LTg5N2UtZTJiYmIyOWEyZWE4&sort=name&layout=list&num=50 GNU 선언문 docbook xml 문서 다운로드]
